 and city streets as you push your reflexes to the limit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/a801dfd78757a49dedce8a87974842c7.poster.avif?t=1726154141\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/a801dfd78757a49dedce8a87974842c7.webm?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/a801dfd78757a49dedce8a87974842c7.mp4?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🏆 <strong>Beat Your Highscore</strong>: Compete against yourself as you strive to beat your high score.<br><br>Get ready for a rush like never before in CyberRush, where the streets are your playground, and every run is a new adventure. Are you up for the challenge? The city awaits your neon-lit fury!",
